root: ^Look, I'm not sure how you got here.
^But, that's okay. You seem pretty inquisitive. That's a really good trait to have.
^People that ask a lot of questions end up with a lot of answers.
^The only way to get back is dying, I think. I don't know though, because I am a sign.
^I am doomed to a placid existence which will outlast humanity and I must suffer in my wooden tomb of language.
^I hope you have a good day, I think. Goodbye.
